If you copy an email address with almost client you will get a string similar to this: "John Doe <john.doe@example.com>"

Now if you paste this string into the User picker of JIRA (one example in Admin helpers), JIRA will not find you the user, even if there is a perfect match for both username and email address.

JIRA should be able to detect and email address format and do a proper search for users.

